Package: nucular
Type: Package
Title: utility functions used for the analysis of genomic nucleosome data
Version: 0.2
Date: 2017
Authors@R: person("Mark", "Heron", email = "heron@genzentrum.lmu.de",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides convienience functions for handling (nucleosomal) genomic data as lists of ff vectors (or vectors).
    The focus lies on comparing the genomic data by computing correlations and other comparison scores between the vector lists.
License: GPL-3
Imports:
